          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BGO"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " It is shaped as a 28 cm long cylinder with a",
                "coaxial hole of a 6 cm diameter. Radial thickness of",
                "the detector is 7 cm. The crystal is optically",
                "divided into six sectors, each covering an azimuthal",
                "angle of 60 degrees.",
                "The detection efficiency for 5.5 MeV gamma-rays is",
                "about 70% with an energy resolution in the total",
                "absorption peak of 8%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To increase the beam current the analyzing magnet was",
                "tuned to select different beams: 1H+, 2H+ and",
                "3H+. In fact the extraction efficiency turned out",
                "to be higher for the molecular beams 1H+ and 3H+."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-SYS",
                "minimum_value": 3.6,
                "maximum_value": 5.3,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The systematic uncertainties ranged",
                "from 3.6% (Eeff = 21.23 keV, highest measured energy)",
                "to 5.3% (Eeff = 2.52 keV, lowest measured energy) and",
                "are negligible in comparison with the accidental errors"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The contribution of natural radioactive isotopes",
                "is visible below 3 MeV"
